#11 (CG) Luna Stillwater [deceased] - Luna, prodigy, savant, of House Stillwater

      The late sister of Aria, and a genius savant who protected her sister with her life.

#13 (CG) Liam [deceased] - peasant of Primwater

      Died in the attempt to rebel against Primwater

      He serves as Ruth's guardian spirit, although neither knows enough to cast magic

#45 (CN) King Alaric III of Distil - Royal King of the lands of Mira, King of Distil

      The king of the lands of Mira who, after 2 of the 14 noble houses (Stillwater and Primwater) suffered great casualties recently, is attempting to manage the chaos of his kingdom. There are 2 noble factions (one more academic and part of the church, and the other more militaristic and part of the military). Stillwater was militaristic, while Primwater was academic, but the King himself allies more with the church.

